title: Dismantled Discography 2002-2007 (192-320kbps mp3)
description:
The (mostly) complete discography of Gary Zon&#039;s one-man electro-industrial band Dismantled. Includes:

Dismantled (192kbps)
Dystopia CDM (192kbps)
PostNuclear (192kbps)
Exit CDM (192kbps)
Breed to Death EP (320kbps)
Standard Issue (320kbps)
Anthem CDM (192kbps)
Thanks For Everything CDM (256kbps)
When I&#039;m Dead (320kbps)
Plus some miscellaneous remixes and stuff

Which is basically everything except Demo Variation and a couple obscure remixes and alternate versions. Enjoy! (and buy the CDs if you like them, et cetera)
